    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is paired with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis retains its signature rigidity with refreshed bushings and a well-damped suspension setup, offering the precise turn-in and analog feedback expected of this platform. This is a well-sorted, driver-quality example ready for the twisties.",
