    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver that has been treated with care. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though closer inspection will reveal minor road-wear such as small stone chips on the front fascia, consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats show only light bolstering wear and are free of any cracks or stains. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced religiously every 5,000 miles, and I have the full documentation to prove it. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes were recently serviced for crisp stopping power. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is an honest car for a discerning buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean history over a showroom-perfect price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
