      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
