      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the variable M differential lock puts power down effectively. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment, maintaining the high-compression engine's peak volumetric efficiency. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in fresh performance rubber, offering the quintessential analog driving experience with precise steering feedback and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution.",
